          },
          "correct": "c",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "(2a+3b)² = (2a)² + 2(2a)(3b) + (3b)² = 4a² + 12ab + 9b²."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch09_B_003",
          "text": "If a + b = 8 and ab = 12, find a² + b²:",
