          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "(4m-3n)² = (4m)² - 2(4m)(3n) + (3n)² = 16m² - 24mn + 9n²."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch09_B_005",
          "text": "Find: (x + 4)(x - 7) using identity (x+a)(x+b) = x² + (a+b)x + ab",
