          "correct": "b",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "105² = (100+5)² = 100² + 2(100)(5) + 5² = 10000 + 1000 + 25 = 11025."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch09_B_007",
          "text": "If x - y = 5 and xy = 14, find x² + y²:",
