            "d": "27"
          },
          "correct": "b",
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "ncert_exemplar",
          "explanation": "x² + 1/x² = (x + 1/x)² - 2 = 5² - 2 = 25 - 2 = 23."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch09_C_003",
          "text": "Find the value of (a - b)² + (b - c)² + (c - a)² when a = 3, b = 5, c = 7:",
          "options": {
            "a": "22",
            "b": "24",
            "c": "26",
            "d": "28"
          },
          "correct": "b",
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "kv_paper",
          "explanation": "(3-5)² + (5-7)² + (7-3)² = (-2)² + (-2)² + 4² = 4 + 4 + 16 = 24."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch09_C_004",
          "text": "The expression (x + y + z)² - (x - y - z)² simplifies to:",
          "options": {
            "a": "4y(y + z)",
            "b": "4x(y + z)",
            "c": "4(xy + xz)",
            "d": "Both b and c"
          },
          "correct": "d",
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "ncert_exemplar",
          "explanation": "(x+y+z)²-(x-y-z)² = [(x+y+z)+(x-y-z)][(x+y+z)-(x-y-z)] = [2x][2y+2z] = 4x(y+z) = 4(xy+xz). Both b and c are correct."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch09_C_005",
          "text": "If a² + b² = 41 and ab = 20, find (a + b) and (a - b):",
          "options": {
            "a": "a+b=9, a-b=1",
            "b": "a+b=9, a-b=±1",
            "c": "a+b=±9, a-b=±1",
            "d": "a+b=81, a-b=1"
          },
          "correct": "c",
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "ncert_exemplar",
          "explanation": "(a+b)² = a²+2ab+b² = 41+40 = 81. a+b = ±9. (a-b)² = a²-2ab+b² = 41-40 = 1. a-b = ±1."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch09_C_006",
          "text": "The area of a rectangle is (x² + 7x + 12) sq units. If its length is (x + 4), its breadth is:",
          "options": {
            "a": "(x + 2)",
            "b": "(x + 3)",
            "c": "(x + 4)",
            "d": "(x + 6)"
          },
          "correct": "b",
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "mp_birla",
          "explanation": "Area = length × breadth. x²+7x+12 = (x+4)×b. b = (x²+7x+12)/(x+4). Factoring: x²+7x+12 = (x+3)(x+4). So b = (x+3)."
        }
      ]
